ey]], English footballer and actor\n*  1978   &ndash; [[Eva Kaili]], Greek journalist and politician\n*  1978   &ndash; [[CM Punk]], American wrestler, mixed martial artist, and actor\n*  1978   &ndash; [[Dave Zastudil]], American football player\n*[[1979]] &ndash; [[Movsar Barayev]], Chechen terrorist (d. 2002)\n*[[1980]] &ndash; [[Cristian Chivu]], Romanian footballer\n*  1980   &ndash; [[Claire Cooper]], English actress\n*  1980   &ndash; [[Koichi Watanabe]], Japanese kick-boxer\n*[[1981]] &ndash; [[Sam Brown (comedian)|Sam Brown]], American actor, producer, and screenwriter\n*  1981   &ndash; [[Martina Schild]], Swiss skier\n*  1981   &ndash; [[Guy Sebastian]], Malaysian-Australian singer-songwriter\n*  1981   &ndash; [[Chou Ssu-Chi]], Taiwanese baseball player\n*[[1982]] &ndash; [[Nicola Adams]], English boxer\n*  1982   &ndash; [[Adam Carroll]], Irish race car driver\n*[[1983]] &ndash; [[Francisco Liriano]], Dominican baseball player\n*  1983   &ndash; [[Dmitri Sychev]], Russian footballer\n*  1983   &ndash; [[Luke Watson]], South African rugby player\n*[[1984]] &ndash; [[Sasha Cohen]], American figure skater\n*  1984   &ndash; [[Adriano Correia]], Brazilian footballer\n*  1984   &ndash; [[Mathieu Cr\u00e9pel]], French snowboarder\n*  1984   &ndash; [[Jefferson Farf\u00e1n]], Peruvian footballer\n*  1984   &ndash; [[Amanda Overmyer]], American singer-songwriter\n*[[1985]] &ndash; [[Andrea Bargnani]], Italian basketball player\n*  1985   &ndash; [[Kafoumba Coulibaly]], Ivorian footballer\n*  1985   &ndash; [[Monta Ellis]], American basketball player\n*  1985   &ndash; [[Kieran Read]], New Zealand rugby player\n*[[1986]] &ndash; [[Ibor Bakar]], French footballer\n*  1986   &ndash; [[Jakub Rze\u017aniczak]], Polish footballer\n*  1986   &ndash; [[Marco Ruben]], Argentinian footballer\n*  1986   &ndash; [[Schoolboy Q]], German-American rapper \n*[[1987]] &ndash; [[Abudramae Bamba]], Ivorian footballer\n*  1987   &ndash; [[Shawn Lauvao]], American football player\n